description: Imprint from colophon. Errata: vol. 1, p. [80]. Engraved title pages for each volume; woodcut head- and tail-pieces; decorative initials. Includes index. Landwehr, J. French, Italian, Spanish, and Portuguese emblem books. Library's c. 1 bound in modern boards; vellum spine and corners; title in black and red ink on spine. Library's c. 2 bound in old vellum; gilt ornaments and designs on front and rear boards; gilt spine; red gilt label on spine; edges sprinkled red and blue; former owner's inscription on front free endpaper recto; later owner's inscription on front free endpaper verso
label: Ferro, Ombre apparenti nel Teatro d'imprese (1629)
